## Complete 3D Window and Door Rendering Pipeline

I've thoroughly explored the 3D rendering system for windows and doors in your modular apartment planner. Here's the complete pipeline from domain model to Three.js mesh:

### Directory Structure (`/c/Users/johnm/modular apartment planner/src/three/`)
```
src/three/
├── scene/
│   ├── buildPreviewScene.js         (Scene assembly orchestrator)
│   ├── objectBuilders.js            (Descriptor builders for all geometry types)
│   └── wallPreviewContext.js        (Wall-relative position calculations)
└── viewer/
    ├── materials.js                 (Material palette definition)
    ├── buildPreviewObjects.js       (Three.js object creation from descriptors)
    ├── createPreviewViewport.js     (WebGL viewport setup)
    ├── disposeScene.js              (Memory cleanup)
    └── ThreePreviewPanel.jsx        (React component integration)
```

